Developer Terms of Use
des:
This skill enables residents of the Vinson Hall Retirement Community to find out what's on the calendar by just asking. When the skill starts, it will tell them what's happening that day, but they can also ask:

- "What's happening tomorrow?" 
- "What's happening on Friday?" 
- "What's happening next week" 

For more on Vinson Hall, please visit: https://www.vinsonhall.org/

This skill was built and is hosted by Witlingo. If you would like your community's calendar to be available to listen to from Alexa, send an email to contact@witlingo.com
